<emphasis id="B91C3D2AA859682AFF807DADFF48F339" box="[95,206,3273,3306]" pageId="4" pageNumber="429">Habitat.</emphasis>
Submontane and possibly montane tropical forest.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
